{"tid":2478630,"cid":7,"subCid":0,"title":"WM俾RBW收購左","createTime":"2021-04-07T08:10:28.000Z","updateTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:36.000Z","uid":316,"like":2,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"b03aa9da059240a796651e9c29d17a00e1cff813","tid":2478630,"uid":316,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:10:28.000Z","msg":"RBW收購OH MY GIRL所屬公司WM娛樂，在IPO前通過M&amp;A加強自身力量<br />\n7日，據投資業界透露，MAMAMOO所屬公司RBW收購了組合OH MY GIRL與ONF所屬公司WM娛樂的經營權。最近，RBW與WM娛樂的最大股東簽訂了股份買賣合同(SPA)，於上月31日完成了交易。 RBW保有了WM娛樂70%以上的股份，並將其編入子公司。<br />\n<br />\nWM娛樂創立於2008年，歌手出身的金正秀代表（藝名:李元敏）既是創立者也是最大股東。主要藝人有OH MY GIRL，B1A4，ONF等。去年銷售額為128億韓元，營業利潤為14億韓元。<br />\nRBW去年創下了歷史最佳業績，銷售額為372億韓元，營業利潤為76億韓元。與前年相比，分別增加了33.7%和48%。 <br />\n目前，RBW的IPO工作正在順利進行中，計劃於今年下半年在KOSDAQ上市。RBW最近在風險投資市場獲得了約1000億韓元以上的企業價值評價，通過此次M&amp;A大幅提高了銷售規模和內容製作能力，因此預計上市後企業價值還會進一步提高。"},{"pid":"a6fb99ffbe1cccb57dd16d840a4b074ac87d3a6a","tid":2478630,"uid":33928,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:23:50.000Z","msg":"爛橋唔好搞鳩人地WM啦<br />\n我記得WM代表幾好<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/pointing.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8c7949682bb28b902a219595824c2c3ffb020397","tid":2478630,"uid":89931,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:25:12.000Z","msg":"WM投共了<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"868459d06f8924c9c4b2f5ffdad94588899375a7","tid":2478630,"uid":8795,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:28:53.000Z","msg":"大公司<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7978b1da14d72058d1889f5db82e8137b676cd34","tid":2478630,"uid":179775,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:41:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />一隊MAMAMOO可以咁勁"},{"pid":"9983f3ab118228c0da6b649c557074f55d340551","tid":2478630,"uid":149371,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-04-07T08:45:36.000Z","msg":"彩演可以做中國女孩🇨🇳💘✊🏼"}]}